        <!-- Welcome information -->
        <div class="topline-container">
            <h1>Welcome to Product Design Game</h1>
            <p>Your mission, should you choose to accept it, is to navigate a product design journey. Acting as a the product manager placed in charge of a new web app, your goal is to get the web app to the best possible start in its first 4 weeks (or 20 working days). </p>
            <!-- TODO: Start by telling us your name -->
